data.description: Comfortable living & city convenience are yours w/this South Tacoma gem! Welcoming covered front porch is the perfect spot to relax out in the fresh air, rain or shine. Inside you’ll find an inviting haven ready for gathering & making memories for years to come. Move right in & add your personal touch to living spaces that provide seamless flow & enjoy the flexibility of 3 bedrooms. Spacious backyard is fully fenced w/room for play toy & gardening, & features outbuilding ideal for storage & projects; transform it into an art studio or home office! Excellent location blocks to Safeway & less than 1 mile to schools, Wapato Park, I-5, Pacific Ave. Easy access to Highway 16 & 512, Downtown Tacoma, Tacoma Dome Station & Joint Base Lewis-McChord.
